OL,3,CStudy finds 'alarming' inequality in
OL,4,Ccare for chronic lung disease patients
OL,6,FBradley Price, director of policy and
OL,7,Fpublic affairs at the charity Action
OL,8,FFor Pulmonary Fibrosis, said the study
OL,9,F"highlights an alarming disparity in
OL,10,Fhealthcare quality and access that
OL,11,Fdemands urgent attention".
OL,13,F"Where you live or your socioeconomic
OL,14,Fstatus should not determine how long
OL,15,Fyou live," he added.
OL,17,F"This is unacceptable. Change is
OL,18,Fneeded to ensure that everyone has
OL,19,Ftimely access to diagnosis, treatment
OL,20,Fand care."
